(21,1,"2019-04-30 03:25:52","2019-04-30 03:25:52","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dear ………………,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;In business, sometimes it\'s hard to see the forest for the trees. You work hard every day to meet your customers\' current needs and anticipate what they\'ll want in the future. You listen carefully, attend to your market, and watch your cash flow. You give your employees the best training and benefits that inspire loyalty. …… Company is a solid business with a good reputation - so what\'s next?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;Growth and innovation are important, but integrating the small picture thinking with the big picture can be tough, especially when you\'re busy with day-to-day transactions and business is consistently good. But could business be great? At Strategy &amp; Shear, we think so.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;You outsource your process trouble shooting, your optimization, your&nbsp;prototyping designs,&nbsp;your research services, and your engineering&nbsp;management including but not limited to&nbsp;•Management of Auxiliary Engineering teams•Optimization of machinery•Identifying failure points•Development of preventive maintenance strategies•Development of standard operation procedures•Management of projects including research and program development•Staff training•Optimization of&nbsp;business operations•</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It&nbsp;makes good financial and business sense to bring in the experts so you can focus on what you do best.&nbsp;Strategy &amp; Shear&nbsp;is the provider of choice that uses research, engineering and business management techniques&nbsp;to integrate&nbsp;the small picture with the big-picture organizational problem solving and creative growth strategy. We\'ll help you think about your business in a whole new way, bringing a fresh perspective to longstanding challenges and helping you envision - and achieve - a future with unlimited possibilities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;We are discrete and our&nbsp;objective is to build on your considerable strengths to ensure that …… Company continues to be a leader in your industry.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;I look forward to meeting with you to discuss next steps.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“Risk</em><em>is on&nbsp;</em><em>the road to success, success is on the road to perfection and perfection is in layers”-&nbsp;</em><em>Olufemi</em><em>E.&nbsp;</em><em>Bamidele</em><em>.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>OlufemiE.&nbsp;Bamidele</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Ph.D, PMP®, PEM™, MBA (In view)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CEO Strategy &amp; Shear</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","overview","","publish","closed","closed","","overview","","","2019-04-30 03:25:52","2019-04-30 03:25:52","",0,"http://motivate-yourself.local/?page_id=21",0,"page","",0),
